Package: daiR
Title: An R Package for Google Document AI
Version: 0.7.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Thomas",
           family = "Hegghammer",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hegghammer@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-6253-1518"))
Description: An R client for the Google Document AI API with additional tools for output 
    file parsing and text reconstruction. Google Document AI is a powerful server-based 
    OCR processor that extracts text and tables from images and pdf files with high 
    accuracy. daiR gives R users programmatic access to this processor and adds several 
    tools to handle and visualize the JSON output from Document AI. See the daiR 
    website for more information and examples.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.0)
